A Fiat não, quando você assina o contrato com ela, naquele momento se decreta o arruinamento da sua paz, da sua estabilidade financeira, sua e da sua família, algo instantânea e ainda muito mais danoso. 
Em nosso aniversário de casamento adquiri pra minha esposa um Fiat Argo Drive 1.0, pior coisa que fiz na minha vida só me trouxe problemas, até que mesmo estando pagas as parcelas a Fiat por alguma razão resolveu apreender o veiculo. Entrou com uma ação de busca e apreensão na justiça e tomou o veiculo. Algo muito semelhante a condutas de bandidos. Aí você pede esclarecimentos a Fiat sobre o que ouve ela não sabe. Em meio à pandemia a Fiat levou o veiculo e trouxe para essa família problemas financeiros gravíssimos, não só pela perca do veiculo, mas pelo que gerou por conta da perca do veiculo; nome sujo, retirada dos filhos da escola particular e colocados na publica, a exposição a pandemia haja vista minha esposa esta tendo que trabalhar de ônibus e são 6 ônibus por dia, não nos foi concedido o PRONAF por conta que o nome de minha esposa ficou com restrição. Hoje vivemos única e exclusivamente do salário da minha esposa em torno de 2 mil onde só a prestação da minha casa é 1600,00 reais. Como viver desça forma. A Fiat consegui destruir toda a vida financeira dessa família. 
O que vocês fizeram nem os piores bandidos fariam.
translation:
For a long time, I believed that society's greatest enemy would be the drug dealers, however after I acquired a Fiat vehicle I discovered, in the worst possible way, that society's number 1 enemy is Fiat. The drug dealer hugs a person, then gradually destroys that person until he contaminates the family. Not Fiat, when you sign the contract with it, at that moment it decrees the ruination of your peace, your financial stability, yours and your family, something instantaneous and even more damaging.
On our wedding anniversary I bought a Fiat Argo Drive 1.0 for my wife, the worst thing I've done in my life only brought me problems, until, even though the installments were paid, Fiat for some reason decided to seize the vehicle. He filed a search and seizure action in court and took the vehicle. Something very similar to bandit conduct. Then you ask Fiat for clarification about what it hears it doesn't know. In the midst of the pandemic, Fiat took the vehicle and brought this family very serious financial problems, not only because of the loss of the vehicle, but because of what it generated due to the loss of the vehicle; dirty name, removal of children from private school and placed in public, exposure to the pandemic as my wife is having to work by bus and there are 6 buses a day, we were not granted PRONAF because my wife's name remained with restriction. Today we live solely and exclusively on my wife's salary of around 2 thousand, where only the installment of my house is 1600.00 reais. How to live this way. Fiat managed to destroy the entire financial life of this family.
What you did not even the worst thugs would do.

comment_text: We loved driving MINIs for years, from a 2003 R50, to our last, a 2020 F54. Sadly we only kept the F54 for less than a year. The adaptive cruise control and collision avoidance were absolutely dangerous. The car would suddenly brake heavily even though there was nothing at all in front of us. That is, if you could even get the adaptive cruise to engage in the first place. BMW needs to up their game. Subaru make a far superior system in similarly priced vehicles.
translation: We loved driving MINIs for years, from a 2003 R50, to our last, a 2020 F54. Sadly we only kept the F54 for less than a year. The adaptive cruise control and collision avoidance were absolutely dangerous. The car would suddenly brake heavily even though there was nothing at all in front of us. That is, if you could even get the adaptive cruise to engage in the first place. BMW needs to up their game. Subaru make a far superior system in similarly priced vehicles.
